{"tid":1399150,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"電視成日見到條女逼條仔儲錢 現實調返轉","createTime":"2019-08-03T05:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:05:19.000Z","uid":53209,"like":14,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"26ef0794e6112ef7e345b72380cb2e01dcdd4878","tid":1399150,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完向西聞記 個女既狂逼個男儲錢結婚買樓 有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實生活中我啱啱調l轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日催眠自己條女叫佢儲錢 佢就一副死老豆咁既款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕新年乜乜柒柒都想去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少少體會到大劉個仔講既去少次日本就買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扣mpf 後 <br />\n<br />\n佢收入大約35000<br />\n6000佢自己屋企家用<br />\n3500我屋企雜費（同住 around7000雜費 一人一半）<br />\n<br />\n我要求佢儲17000 其實都唔算太過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n利申：收入相約  對自己更加嚴謹 月儲超過佢"},{"pid":"e269693af460033031c4a282c3f90582e2b94c7f","tid":1399150,"uid":73660,"like":81,"dislike":35,"score":46,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"人地點洗錢都要你管，男人老狗咪咁婆媽啦。咁有能力就自己買"},{"pid":"273fb68a31d966a7b75c587ad5569e6a034f898e","tid":1399150,"uid":254551,"like":49,"dislike":5,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"佢要求你儲$70000都唔過份丫"},{"pid":"3c684c936b575889dde5f1790cf7cc69c831f15d","tid":1399150,"uid":53209,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"e269693af460033031c4a282c3f90582e2b94c7f","tid":1399150,"uid":73660,"like":81,"dislike":35,"score":